   TV-SURFER UPN airs the new ``Mercy Point'' (an ``ER'' in space
with aliens (and as weird as it sounds)) plus ``Moesha'' and
``Clueless.'' (Atlanta Journal-Constitution) ETA: 6 p.m.
</P>
