until Nov. 14 and $175 through Jan. 3, (800) 699-1201; Rittenhouse
Hotel, $299 Monday through Thursday and $245 Friday through Sunday,
(215) 546-9000; Ritz-Carlton, $309 Monday through Thursday and $269
Friday through Sunday, (215) 563-1600, and Warwick Hotel, $229
until Nov. 14 and $199 through Jan. 3, (215) 735-6000.
</P>
<P>
