<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-05 18:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0510 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CALIF-FONG-HNS &LR;      10-05 0871
