<P>
   &UR; IS THIS DIRTY? &LR;
</P>
<P>
   The Dean of Women at an exclusive girls' school was lecturing
her students on sexual morality. `We live today in very difficult
times for young people. In moments of temptation,` she said, `ask
yourself just one question: Is an hour of pleasure worth a lifetime
of shame?`
</P>
<P>
   A young woman rose in the back of the room and said, `Excuse me,
but how do you make it last an hour?`
</P>
<P>
   &UR; KIDS &LR;
</P>
<P>
   Johnny watched, fascinated, as his mother smoothed cold cream on
her face.
</P>
<P>
   `Why do you do that, mommy?` he asked.
</P>
<P>
   `To make myself beautiful,` said his mother, who then began
removing the cream with a tissue.
</P>
<P>
   `What's the matter?` asked Little Johnny. `Giving up?`
</P>
